---
config:
  theme: dark
  layout: dagre
---
flowchart TD
    A[Start: Receive Batch Request] --> B{Valid files uploaded?}
    B -->|No| C[Return 400 Error]
    B -->|Yes| D[Extract Device Fingerprint]
    D --> E[Get/Create User]
    E --> F[Create ScanBatch]
    F --> G[Process Images Loop]
    
    subgraph "Process Each Image"
        G --> H[Save Image to Storage]
        H --> I[Create ScanImage Record]
        I --> J[Run Detection Model]
        J --> K{Seeds Detected?}
        K -->|No| L[Continue to Next Image]
        K -->|Yes| M[Classify Each Seed]
        M --> N[Create SeedDetection Records]
        N --> L
    end
    
    L --> O{More Images?}
    O -->|Yes| G
    O -->|No| P[Aggregate Statistics]
    P --> Q[Update ScanBatch Status]
    Q --> R[Return JSON Response]
    R --> S[End]
